"body":"這，這也沒什麼好大驚小怪的吧！？\n比起這個！　都怪你們太晚到了\n所以再不快點出發就要遲到了！　都給我加快腳步！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"真，真是厲害的演奏……\n從頭到尾是非常震撼……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"對啊，雖然我們學校那邊\n偶爾也會有機會去聽古典音樂會，\n但我還真沒有聽過像那種等級的演奏－……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"CHU²媽媽只拉了一個音，\n整個會場的氣氛就完全變了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"那就是世界水準的演奏啊……\n讓所有聽的人都沉醉在其中的演奏，\n指的就是那麼一回事吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"……你們每個人都被征服了呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"這也難免啊，親耳聽到那種演奏鐵定會這樣吧？\n該怎麼說呢，就是有種等級完全不同的感覺……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"你說的完全沒錯。\n聽完那種級別的演奏還沒有任何反應的話，\n那就太讓人懷疑有沒有作為音樂人的Potential了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"……But，我們昨天的演奏，\n讓那個等級的音樂家說了「獲得了刺激」……不是嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"全體","body":"……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Mom面對音樂的時候絕對不會說謊。\n既然我們能讓那樣的Mom，說他得到了「刺激」，\n意思就是RAS的演奏也有那個水準","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"然後我們，是遲早要讓世間懂得什麼叫「最強」音樂的樂團。\n既然如此，我們根本沒時間在這邊磨蹭了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"ev172-ep2-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"charac